#. <section class="sutta" id="sn6.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Parinibbānasutta → parinibbāṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Parinibbānasutta"
msgstr "15. Final Extinguishment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.158"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kusinārāyaṃ viharati upavattane mallānaṃ sālavane "
"antarena yamakasālānaṃ parinibbānasamaye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying between a pair of sal trees in the sal "
"forest of the Mallas at Upavattana near Kusinārā at the time of his final "
"extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.3"
msgid "“handa dāni, bhikkhave, āmantayāmi vo:"
msgstr "“Come now, mendicants, I say to you all:"

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.4"
msgid "‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā, appamādena sampādethā’”ti."
msgstr "Conditions fall apart. Persist with diligence.”"

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ tathāgatassa pacchimā vācā."
msgstr "These were the Realized One’s last words."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ → paṭhamajjhānaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts2)
#. VAR: Paṭhamā jhānā → paṭhamajjhānā (bj, s1-3, km, pts2) | pathamajhānā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.15:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā "
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. "
"Tatiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā "
"vuṭṭhahitvā ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākāsānañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā "
"viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Viññāṇañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ "
"samāpajji. Ākiñcaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. "
"Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajji."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha entered the first absorption. Emerging from that, he entered "
"the second absorption. Emerging from that, he successively entered into and "
"emerged from the third absorption, the fourth absorption, the dimension of "
"infinite space, the dimension of infinite consciousness, the dimension of "
"nothingness, and the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. "
"Then he entered the cessation of perception and feeling."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.341"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:3.1"
msgid ""
"Saññāvedayitanirodhā vuṭṭhahitvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. "
"Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. "
"Ākiñcaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Viññāṇañcāyatanā "
"vuṭṭhahitvā ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākāsānañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā "
"catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ "
"samāpajji. Tatiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā "
"vuṭṭhahitvā paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā dutiyaṃ "
"jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Tatiyā "
"jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā "
"samanantaraṃ bhagavā parinibbāyi."
msgstr ""
"Then he emerged from the cessation of perception and feeling and entered the "
"dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. Emerging from that, he "
"successively entered into and emerged from the dimension of nothingness, the "
"dimension of infinite consciousness, the dimension of infinite space, the "
"fourth absorption, the third absorption, the second absorption, and the "
"first absorption. Emerging from that, he successively entered into and "
"emerged from the second absorption and the third absorption. Then he entered "
"the fourth absorption. Emerging from that the Buddha immediately became "
"fully extinguished."

msgctxt "sn6.15:3.2"
msgid ""
"Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā brahmā sahampati imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha became fully extinguished, along with the full "
"extinguishment, Brahmā Sahampati recited this verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.1"
msgid "“Sabbeva nikkhipissanti,"
msgstr "“All creatures in this world"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.2"
msgid "bhūtā loke samussayaṃ;"
msgstr "must lay their body down."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.3"
msgid "Yattha etādiso satthā,"
msgstr "For even a Teacher such as this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.4"
msgid "loke appaṭipuggalo;"
msgstr "unrivaled in the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.5"
msgid "Tathāgato balappatto,"
msgstr "the Realized One, attained to power,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.6"
msgid "sambuddho parinibbuto”ti."
msgstr "the Buddha became fully extinguished.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.342"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:5.1"
msgid ""
"Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā sakko devānamindo imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Sakka, lord of gods, recited this "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.1"
msgid "“Aniccā vata saṅkhārā,"
msgstr "“Oh! Conditions are impermanent,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.2"
msgid "uppādavayadhammino;"
msgstr "their nature is to rise and fall;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.3"
msgid "Uppajjitvā nirujjhanti,"
msgstr "having arisen, they cease;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.4"
msgid "tesaṃ vūpasamo sukho”ti."
msgstr "their stilling is true bliss.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:7.1"
msgid ""
"Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā āyasmā ānando imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Venerable Ānanda recited this "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.1"
msgid "“Tadāsi yaṃ bhiṃsanakaṃ,"
msgstr "“Then there was terror!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.2"
msgid "tadāsi lomahaṃsanaṃ;"
msgstr "Then they had goosebumps!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.3"
msgid "Sabbākāravarūpete,"
msgstr "When the Buddha, endowed with all fine qualities,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.4"
msgid "sambuddhe parinibbute”ti."
msgstr "became fully extinguished.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.159"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:9.1"
msgid ""
"Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā āyasmā anuruddho imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Venerable Anuruddha recited this "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.1"
msgid "“Nāhu assāsapassāso,"
msgstr "“There was no more breathing"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.2"
msgid "ṭhitacittassa tādino;"
msgstr "for the poised one of steady heart."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.3"
msgid "Anejo santimārabbha,"
msgstr "Imperturbable, committed to peace,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.4"
msgid "cakkhumā parinibbuto."
msgstr "the seer became fully extinguished."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.1"
msgid "Asallīnena cittena,"
msgstr "He put up with painful feelings"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.2"
msgid "vedanaṃ ajjhavāsayi;"
msgstr "without flinching."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.3"
msgid "Pajjotasseva nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "The liberation of his heart"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.4"
msgid "vimokkho cetaso ahū”ti."
msgstr "was like the extinguishing of a lamp.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.5"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.343"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.1"
msgid "Brahmāsanaṃ devadatto,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.2"
msgid "Andhakavindo aruṇavatī;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.3"
msgid "Parinibbānena ca desitaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.4"
msgid "Idaṃ brahmapañcakanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.5"
msgid "Brahmasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Brahmā are complete."
